‘Merican Yo-kai have made their way to the YO-KAI WATCH 3 game and they’re rootin’ tootin’ troublemakers. Speaking of troublemakers, in the town of BBQ, zombies run wild after dark and Nate must stop them in the all-new Zombie Night mode.
